Package com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.reflect

Class ImplementationRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.reflect.ImplementationRegistry
  • public class ImplementationRegistry
extends Object
    Central registry for all custom user implementations. This class will look for custom implementations that override the default implementation of this framework. Supports the following interfaces:
    • SettingsProvider
    • PermissionsProvider
    • HelpMessageFactory
    • ErrorMessageFactory
    • Router
    • MessageSender
    • TypeAdapter
    • Filter
    • Validator
    Since:
    2.0.0
    Version:
    2.2.0
    Author:
    Kaktushose
    See Also:
